org.jemmy.fx.control

Class TextInputControlWrap<T extends javafx.scene.control.TextInputControl>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jemmy.control.Wrap<T>
      • org.jemmy.fx.NodeWrap<T>
        • org.jemmy.fx.control.ControlWrap<T>
          • org.jemmy.fx.control.TextInputControlWrap<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.jemmy.control.ScreenArea, org.jemmy.interfaces.CaretOwner, org.jemmy.interfaces.ControlInterface, org.jemmy.interfaces.Focusable, org.jemmy.interfaces.IntervalSelectable, org.jemmy.interfaces.KeyTarget, org.jemmy.interfaces.Label, org.jemmy.interfaces.MouseTarget, org.jemmy.interfaces.Text

    @ControlType(value=javafx.scene.control.TextInputControl.class)
@ControlInterfaces(value=org.jemmy.input.SelectionText.class)
@DockInfo(generateSubtypeLookups=true)
public class TextInputControlWrap<T extends javafx.scene.control.TextInputControl>
extends ControlWrap<T>
implements org.jemmy.interfaces.Text, org.jemmy.interfaces.IntervalSelectable, org.jemmy.interfaces.Focusable
    Test support for Java FX text editing controls. Supported operations are: type, clean, select, move caret - all that is supported in SelectionText control interface. See TextSample for more info.
    Author:
    shura
    See Also:
    SelectionText
